{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MBMTileStoreUsageMode@MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate","roleHeading":"Case","symbolKind":"case","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"readAndUpdate"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapboxMaps"}],"title":"TileStoreUsageMode.readAndUpdate"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tile store enabled for accessing local tile packs and for loading new tile packs from server."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode\/readAndUpdate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readAndUpdate","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All tile requests are converted to tile pack requests, i.e.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the tile pack that includes the request tile will be loaded, and the tile extracted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"from it. In this mode, no individual tile requests will be made."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This mode can be useful if the map trajectory is predefined and the user cannot pan","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"freely (e.g. navigation use cases), so that there is a good chance tile packs are already loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"